10. Common Beginner Mistakes
Mistake 1

Using lowercase component name

❌

function header() {}

✅

function Header() {}
Mistake 2

Forgetting return

❌

function Header() {
  <h1>Hello</h1>;
}

Nothing appears.

✅

function Header() {
  return <h1>Hello</h1>;
}
Mistake 3

Not exporting component

❌

function Header() {}

Cannot import elsewhere.

✅

export default Header;
